---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Tags from "../components/Tags.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sboonny Portfolio | Home">
  <Header />
  <main
    class="prose mx-auto mt-8 max-w-7xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-400 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
      Sboonny
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
      A front end Developer who enjoys contributing to open source projects. I
      work mainly with <span class="font-bold text-blue-600">TypeScript</span>
       and <span class="font-bold text-blue-400">React</span>.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h2 class="dark:text-slate-100">About</h2>
      <p>
        I have always wanted to be a programmer, but whatever tools or course I
        used to learn programming, end with my disappointment. Tried to focus on
        business to earn living, but who known that my interaction with business
        will guide me to <a
          class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
          href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hp1INWuXIgo&pp=ygUaY29mZmVlemlsbGEgZnJlZSBjb2RlIGNhbXA%3D"
          rel="noreferrer noopener"
          target="_blank">freeCodeCamp</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
    <div
      class="relative flex gap-2 p-3 hover:bg-slate-200 hover:bg-opacity-10 hover:shadow-sm"
    >
      <span
        class="w-40 break-keep text-stone-700 opacity-80 after:w-full after:text-slate-100 dark:text-stone-300 lg:w-28"
        >2022-SEP 2023</span
      >
      <div>
        <a
          class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] before:absolute before:inset-0 before:h-full before:w-full hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
          href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Frontend Dev - freeCodeCamp</a
        >
        <p>
          I previously worked on freeCodeCamp as a maintainer, my focus was
          clearing the front end tasks there.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section>
      <h2 class="my-12 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
        Projects that I worked on with others ü§ù.
      </h2>
      <div class="grid gap-3 grid-cols-fit">
        <div class="relative bg-slate-700 p-5 shadow-lg">
          <a
            href=""
            class="text-slate-300 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:h-full before:w-full hover:text-slate-400 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100"
            >Chapter</a
          >
          <p class="mb-0 text-slate-300">
            I was lucky to have worked in chapter with awesome collages, and
            talented individuals who contributed to that codebase.
          </p>
          <Tags
            tags={[
              "TypeScript",
              "NextJS",
              "React",
              "Prisma",
              "Chakra UI",
              "GraphQL",
              "Apollo",
            ]}
          />
        </div>

        <div class="relative bg-slate-700 p-5 shadow-lg">
          <a
            href=""
            class="text-slate-300 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:h-full before:w-full hover:text-slate-400 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100"
            >freeCodeCamp</a
          >
          <p class="text-slate-300">
            an open source community that helps you learn to code, build
            projects, and earn certifications.
          </p>
          <Tags
            tags={[
              "TypeScript",
              "Gasby",
              "React",
              "Prisma",
              "Fastify",
              "Tailwind"
            ]}
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Worked on <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter/pull/2301"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">implementing search function</a
          > using React `useState` as state management.
        </li>
        <li>
          Paired on fixing loading of the data bug in the homepage, and <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter/pull/2340"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">removed the extra query</a
          >.
        </li>
        <li>
          Worked on making chapter responsive, you can check it by running a <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://gitpod.io/#https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/chapter"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Gitpod</a
          > instance.
        </li>
        <li>
          Worked on <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pull/50286"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Restful API, and implemented test</a
          > for it.
        </li>
        <li>
          Helped freeCodeCamp issue by implementing <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3ASboonny+is%3Aclosed+"
            >small pull requests</a
          > that solves issue in small steps.
        </li>
        <li>
          Helped with rewrite of the old API to a <a
            class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 text-slate-700 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:text-slate-500 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
            href="https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/freeCodeCamp/pulls?q=is%3Apr+label%3A%22platform%3A+api%22+author%3ASboonny+is%3Aclosed"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Fastify</a
          > based one.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">
        Project I like, and have contributed to
      </h2>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Create T3 App</h3>
        <p>
          I like this project, because of how easy it makes my life, when
          creating a quick project for my friends or in freelance projects.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pull/1051"
              >Reverted border.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pull/1019"
              >Reverted link icon.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pull/954"
              >Align search modal spacing.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pull/988"
              >Align the file structure.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pull/1032"
              >Consistent Create T3 App reference.</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              class="rounded-sm border-b border-slate-400 font-bold text-slate-900 transition-[border-color] hover:border-slate-600 hover:no-underline dark:text-slate-100 dark:hover:border-slate-50"
              href="https://github.com/t3-oss/create-t3-app/pulls?q=is%3Apr+author%3ASboonny+is%3Aclosed++proofread"
              >Proofread Arabic translation</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
